  "description": "Comprehensive annual health assessment covering vital signs, lifestyle factors, current medications, wellbeing screening, and clinician follow-up. Demonstrates: version, publisher, prefix, item.code[], minValue/maxValue, rendering-style, calculatedExpression (BMI), sdc-questionnaire-hidden (bmi-high-flag — hidden boolean drives enableWhen), sliderStepValue, repeats+minOccurs/maxOccurs (medications is required to satisfy R4 context invariant), ordinalValue, enableWhen, initial[], maxLength, and questionnaire-constraint.",
